But the players are human beings,so sometimes they make mistakes that costs the game. For me key fact is... gomez or lovren  not world class.lovren naot anymore  due to his age. snippet.textDisplay: Klopp: "I am not concerned about the momentum"... "So many good things, Adam running like crazy"... Well, LFC midfield sure running like crazy, that is one of the reason they losing games after games. Three loss in four games is not acceptable. Especially, when they can not score one goal!.. Because of the poor midfield, the defence, especially Trent and Robbo has to support the offensive line to make something going, but with fast teams you can get punished in a hurry... CrazyKlopp paid a staggering amount of money, 131.45m pounds for his three complete flops: Keita, Fabinho and Oxlade. And the rest of the midfield is not much better: Hendo, Vijnaldum and teacher's pet Adam is not reliable. Only the 33-years-old Milner is putting in everything he has. Going back to the past four games, the most worrying issue is the disappearing fighter spirit, and serious attitude problems. There are players don't like each other at all, especially the big rivalry between Salah and Mane is not helpful. Salah had problems with his selfishness before, basically at every club he played for. Klopp should have fixed in-club problems long time ago. Anyway, it's time to shape up, or the rest of the season will be very ugly.
